flowchart TD
    A[ConfigPipeline: merge Navigation2D + playground constants] --> B[Navigation2DRuntime.CloneValidated]
    B --> C[Steady-state SoA sync marks dirty agents]
    C --> D[Nav2DCellMap.UpdatePositions]
    D --> E{Cell migrations exceed adaptive threshold?}
    E -->|yes| F[Clear and rebuild full cell map]
    E -->|no| G[Incremental detach/attach update]
    F --> H[Budgeted neighbor queries]
    G --> H
    H --> I{Avoidance mode}
    I -->|ORCA| J[ORCA solve]
    I -->|Sonar| K[Sonar solve]
    I -->|Hybrid| L[Hybrid gate then ORCA/Sonar]
    J --> M[Write desired velocity + HUD counters]
    K --> M
    L --> M
    E -->|no explicit config / wrong mode| X[Failure branch: tombstones accumulate and hitch returns]
